  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6989 trading just below the massive 7000 gamma wall (+17.3B), dealers are positioned to aggressively sell any push above this level while providing strong support on dips toward 6975. The PIN regime and concentrated positive gamma structure above spot creates a powerful mean-reversion setup, with dealers acting as liquidity providers against momentum. Watch 7000 as the critical resistance where dealer selling pressure intensifies, and 6878 GEX flip as the key support threshold below which the regime shifts bearish.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect strong resistance at 7000 with pullbacks getting bought.",
